name: Echos 0-215
description:
Imperfect echos of shape and color.

Echos is a generative artwork minted on fx(hash) in December, 2021. Each output is unique with different features (color, number of lines, orientation, etc) that are determined by the transaction hash.

This is an image of all 215 mints plus the preview image (top-left). Mints are arranged in ascending order from #1 to #215, going from left-to-right and top-to-bottom.
